{
  "info": {
    "name": "Haunt API",
    "description": "Cryptocurrency data API with real-time WebSocket updates",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "haunt-api"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3001",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/health",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "health"]
            },
            "description": "Check server health status, including cache and scheduler status."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "description": "Health check endpoints"
    },
    {
      "name": "Crypto",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Listings",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/crypto/listings?start=1&limit=100&sort=market_cap&sort_dir=desc",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "crypto", "listings"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "start",
                  "value": "1",
                  "description": "Starting position (1-indexed)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "100",
                  "description": "Number of results (max 500)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "sort",
                  "value": "market_cap",
                  "description": "Sort field"
                },
                {
                  "key": "sort_dir",
                  "value": "desc",
                  "description": "Sort direction (asc/desc)"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Get a paginated list of cryptocurrencies sorted by market cap."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Search Cryptos",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/crypto/search?q=bitcoin&limit=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "crypto", "search"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "q",
                  "value": "bitcoin",
                  "description": "Search query (name or symbol)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "20",
                  "description": "Max results (default 20)"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Search cryptocurrencies by name or symbol."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Crypto by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/crypto/1",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "crypto", "1"]
            },
            "description": "Get a single cryptocurrency by its CoinMarketCap ID."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Crypto Quotes",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/crypto/1/quotes",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "crypto", "1", "quotes"]
            },
            "description": "Get latest quotes for a cryptocurrency."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "description": "Cryptocurrency data endpoints"
    },
    {
      "name": "Market",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Global Metrics",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/market/global",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "market", "global"]
            },
            "description": "Get global cryptocurrency market metrics including total market cap, BTC dominance, etc."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Fear & Greed Index",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/market/fear-greed",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "market", "fear-greed"]
            },
            "description": "Get the current Fear & Greed Index value and classification."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "description": "Market-wide data endpoints"
    },
    {
      "name": "WebSocket",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "WebSocket Connection",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Upgrade",
                "value": "websocket"
              },
              {
                "key": "Connection",
                "value": "Upgrade"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "ws://localhost:3001/ws",
              "protocol": "ws",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "3001",
              "path": ["ws"]
            },
            "description": "WebSocket connection for real-time updates.\n\n## Subscribe to Assets\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"subscribe\",\n  \"assets\": [\"btc\", \"eth\", \"sol\"]\n}\n```\n\n## Unsubscribe from Assets\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"unsubscribe\",\n  \"assets\": [\"btc\"]\n}\n```\n\n## Server Messages\n\n### Price Update\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"price_update\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"symbol\": \"btc\",\n    \"price\": 50000,\n    \"change24h\": 2.5,\n    \"volume24h\": 25000000000,\n    \"timestamp\": \"2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Market Update\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"market_update\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"totalMarketCap\": 2000000000000,\n    \"totalVolume24h\": 100000000000,\n    \"btcDominance\": 45,\n    \"timestamp\": \"2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z\"\n  }\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "description": "WebSocket endpoints for real-time data"
    }
  ]
}
